              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Both Single Foils and Stacks of Three to Six Foils",
                "Were Used For the Irradiations.",
                "The Energy Degradation by Absorbers (WINDOW, AIR,",
                "AND TARGET) Was Calculated According to",
                "L.C.Northcliffe Et Al.,Nucl.Data,A7,233(1970) And",
                "C.F.Williamson Et Al. Cea-R-3042(1966)"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "EN-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Energy Uncertainty -",
                "The Energy Errors are Typically About 100 KeV and",
                "Include the Uncertainties in the Beam Energy, in the",
                "Energy Loss Calculations For Each Absorber and Target,",
                "And the Energy Straggling. Corrections For Energy",
                "Resolution Due to the Finite Target Thicknesses were",
                "Negligible."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Data Uncertainty -",
                "The Errors of the Cross Sections Include",
                "Uncertainties from Peak Analyses (INCLUDING COUNTING",
                "STATISTICS, ALWAYS BELOW 3%), Decay Curve Analyses",
                " (TYPICALLY BELOW 3%), Absolute Detector Efficiencies",
                " (5 TO 10%), Gamma-Ray Abundances (1 TO 4%), Target",
                "Thicknesses (1.0 TO 1.5%), and Current Integration",
                " (ABOUT 1%)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The Authors have Made a Compilation to Compare Their",
